  "remarks": "Naser MALEKI was listed pursuant to paragraph 12 of resolution 1737 (2006), as read with resolutions 1747, 1803 and 1929, as: a person involved in nuclear or ballistic missile activities. Head of SHIG, which is designated under resolution 1737 (2006) for its role in Iran’s ballistic missile programme. Naser Maleki is also a MODAFL official overseeing work on the Shahab-3 ballistic missile programme. The Shahab-3 is Iran’s long range ballistic missile currently in service. The Director Disqualification Sanction was imposed on 09/04/2025.",
  "@context": "https://www.ammitto.org/ontology/context.jsonld"
}